From 8cce2ccc45cfedd903197cb72921edddeba441a0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Marcello Sylvester Bauer <marcello.bauer@9elements.com>
Date: Sun, 15 Feb 2026 13:17:26 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] fansensor: add fan fault monitoring via hwmon fault attribute

Poll hwmon fan*_fault sysfs attributes every 5 seconds and update
OperationalStatus.Functional in phosphor inventory on state changes.
Emit Redfish ResourceEvent log entries for fault and recovery events.

Signed-off-by: Marcello Sylvester Bauer <marcello.bauer@9elements.com>
---
 src/fan/FanFault.cpp | 133 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 src/fan/FanFault.hpp |  48 ++++++++++++++++
 src/fan/FanMain.cpp  |  25 +++++++-
 src/fan/meson.build  |   1 +
 4 files changed, 205 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 src/fan/FanFault.cpp
 create mode 100644 src/fan/FanFault.hpp

diff --git a/src/fan/FanFault.cpp b/src/fan/FanFault.cpp
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..fd60339
--- /dev/null
+++ b/src/fan/FanFault.cpp
@@ -0,0 +1,133 @@
+/*
